OL,3,CPolice and Crime Commissioner for
OL,4,CHampshire to run for mayor
OL,6,FHampshire and the Isle of Wight Police
OL,7,Fand Crime Commissioner has announced
OL,8,Fshe intends to stand to become one of
OL,9,Fthe region's first directly-elected
OL,10,FMayors.
OL,12,FDonna Jones hopes to be the
OL,13,FConservative candidate for the new
OL,14,Fposition of Mayor of Hampshire and the
OL,15,FSolent, in 2026.
OL,17,FThe government launched a public
OL,18,Fconsultation on devolution and the
OL,19,Fidea of a strategic combined authority
OL,20,FMonday on 17 February.
